      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry is a recognized surrogate for Class II CPB devices. Operating envelope (2–7 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) spans the CPB clinical range. Validation activities directly support the COU at MRL 2."
    },
