      "acceptanceCriteria": "Power-law hemolysis model and turbulence model selection must be justified against available literature for rotating blood-contacting devices.",
      "rationale": "Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model selected based on published validation studies for centrifugal blood pumps. k-omega SST turbulence model justified by published comparative studies on FDA benchmark. Model form uncertainty acknowledged and bounded within acceptable limits for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
